Output .github/demo.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 13
Set Width 1200
Set Height 620
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 15
Set TypingSpeed 50ms
Set CursorBlink false
Set PlaybackSpeed 1

Hide
Type "export PATH=/Users/jacob/Desktop/flowtriq/nethawk/bin:$PATH"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Show

Type "nethawk -demo"
Enter
Sleep 26s
Type "q"
Sleep 500ms
